# restaurant-client

A lightweight Python client for the **Foursquare Places API** to search for restaurants and explore nearby food options.

---

## Features

- Simple restaurant search by **query + location**
- Optional filters (limit, radius, categories, etc.)
- Returns results as a **pandas DataFrame** (easy for analysis)
- Reads API keys safely via **environment variables** (`python-dotenv`)

---

## Installation

### From TestPyPI (recommended for testing)

```bash
pip install -i https://test.pypi.org/simple/ restaurant-client

